title: 2007 eBay Startup Guide - Entreprenuer Magazine (2nd edition)
description:
This is a great resource for anyone thinking of making money on ebay. I am uploading this because I am boycotting eBay, and no longer care if there is more competition on ebay due to the sharing of this magazine. 

I scanned this in myself a while ago, and now am sharing this with the world! This is my first torrent upload.

For more information on the eBay boycott, visit this youtube video and see the links in the description panel.
